Code of Conduct for Small Software Engineering Team

Respect and professionalism:
Treat all team members with respect and dignity.
Act professionally and maintain high work ethics.

Communication and teamwork:
Maintain open and honest communication.
Collaborate effectively with the team.
Support each other and work towards common goals.

Quality and accountability:
Deliver high-quality work.
Take responsibility for actions and decisions.
Meet deadlines and communicate promptly on any delays or issues.

Continuous improvement:
Continuously improve skills and knowledge.
Stay current with new technologies and industry trends.

Diversity and inclusion:
Embrace diversity and respect differences.
Foster a diverse and inclusive environment.
Support the growth and development of all team members.

Confidentiality and ethics:
Protect sensitive information and maintain confidentiality.
Act ethically and responsibly at all times.